## Architectural Decisions (Agreed)


| Decision                | Choice                                   | Rationale                                                                                                                                                                      |
| ----------------------- | ---------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| Provenance persistence  | Redis + PostgreSQL hybrid                | Real-time access during workflow via Redis; flush to PostgreSQL on completion for audit queries. Matches existing Redis-first pattern.                                         |
| Output adapter strategy | Static mapping + LLM extraction fallback | Maximum resilience against LLM output field variability. Static paths cover 90% of cases; LLM fallback handles edge cases.                                                     |
| Consistency checker     | Extend HaluGate NLI engine               | Reuses the existing claim extraction and numeric verification infrastructure. Adds cross-agent comparison as a new mode alongside the existing narrative-vs-ground-truth mode. |


