### 1.5 Failure Modes


| Failure Point                               | Current Behavior                            | Post-Fix Behavior                                                                         |
| ------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Tool API error (e.g., Finnhub 401)          | Silent failure or crash                     | Warning in agent output; data point marked `[ESTIMATED]` with methodology                 |
| LLM rate limit hit                          | Request fails, no fallback                  | Gateway retries with backoff → falls back to next provider in chain                       |
| Redis unavailable during workflow           | N/A (new)                                   | Provenance records buffered in-memory, flushed to PostgreSQL directly on completion       |
| Output adapter can't map a field            | Scorer gets zero, produces misleading score | Field marked `unavailable`, scorer reduces confidence on that component                   |
| Consistency check finds contradiction       | Not detected until end (HaluGate)           | Soft warning logged, propagated to Red Team + Scorer + Report                             |
| Local LLM produces malformed JSON tool call | Silent tool-call failure                    | JSON repair attempted; if repair fails, agent proceeds without tool data and logs warning |


